# Roadmap tracking

## Sources of truth

| Surface | Role |
|---------|------|
| `docs/ROADMAP.md` | Human **Now / Next / Later** (max 3 Now, 5 Done) |
| `docs/brain_dump.md` | Inbox — triage weekly into ROADMAP |
| `.omg/workflow-manifest.json` | Agent spec/plan lifecycle only |
| GitHub issues | Blocker detail + portfolio history (`type:*`, `area:*`) |

## Agent commands

```bash
uv run python scripts/roadmap.py agent    # priority view (run before planning)
uv run python scripts/roadmap.py validate # after editing ROADMAP.md
make roadmap-check                        # validate + pytest
```

## Rules

1. **Prefer ROADMAP Now** over manifest when picking the next task.
2. Use manifest + `.omg/specs|plans/` only for multi-step agent execution.
3. **Do not** mirror issue bodies or evidence into ROADMAP — one-line rows + links only.
4. On completion: close GitHub issue, move row to **Done** (trim to 5), update manifest if linked.
5. CI fails if Now > 3, Done > 5, or required sections are missing.

## Git

Commit verified roadmap/issue updates locally; push only when the user asks.
